<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-81-0802 </DOCNO><TEXT>The results of measurements of the component distribution over Cd/subx/Hg/sub 1-x/Te crystal surface (x=0.16) after local mechanical deformationsare given. It is shown that mechanical disturbances of Cd/sub x/Hg/sub1-x/Te crystal structure lead to local decomposition of the solid solutioneither during mechanical action or in the successive crystal storagewith disturbances under natural conditions.</TEXT></DOC>